  "detailed_description": "<strong>Stranded on a frigid mining outpost, you must protect the reactor that powers your distress beacon from hordes of gloops- squishy slimes that attack with plasma projectiles! Collect items, set up sentries, defeat bosses, and fight to survive in this highly replayable twin-stick wave-defense roguelike.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT</h2>Defend the outpost from relentless swarms of enemies. Play from a cast of grizzled mercenaries, each with unique weapons, items, and abilities! Dodge attacks by combat rolling and make every bullet count!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/3b64230c9a448837020af752f7f77f2a.poster.avif?t=1763958459\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/3b64230c9a448837020af752f7f77f2a.webm?t=1763958459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/3b64230c9a448837020af752f7f77f2a.mp4?t=1763958459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUY</h2>Spend scrap at shops to buy curious items and increase your fighting power. Pick up items that synergize well with each other to create a limitless number of unique builds. Take your chances with the store's random option to get legendary items for cheap. Complete challenging achievements to unlock new items, playable characters, and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/e0bf2eb1acadf8dfce415aabb3faedc9.poster.avif?t=1763958459\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/e0bf2eb1acadf8dfce415aabb3faedc9.webm?t=1763958459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/e0bf2eb1acadf8dfce415aabb3faedc9.mp4?t=1763958459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PREPARE</h2>Adapt to survive as enemies break through barricades and find new paths to attack from. Utilize teleporters, vents, doors, and a drawbridge to control the flow of combat and give yourself an edge in battle. You can also spend scrap on sentry turrets and automated drones to bolster your defenses!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/20a92180d7694c2cd532eec74601b016.poster.avif?t=1763958459\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/20a92180d7694c2cd532eec74601b016.webm?t=1763958459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/20a92180d7694c2cd532eec74601b016.mp4?t=1763958459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE</h2><br>Shoot, dodge, and blast your way to victory as you defend the outpost's reactor until reinforcements arrive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/5c72c38335502fb18c6d9ae9f7e1a396.poster.avif?t=1763958459\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/5c72c38335502fb18c6d9ae9f7e1a396.webm?t=1763958459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/5c72c38335502fb18c6d9ae9f7e1a396.mp4?t=1763958459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
